This paper discusses the use of machine learning and deep learning techniques in networking and traffic control, which falls under the category of computer networks and internet architecture (cs.NI). The paper also mentions the extraction of knowledge from collected data, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of knowledge to improve system intelligence and communication also relates to control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the potential for KCN to improve security, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
